Recommends: libayatana-appindicator3-1
Description: Automate mouse movement and keyboard actions on Linux
 Move Mouse is a utility that periodically moves the mouse cursor and
 simulates keyboard input to prevent screensavers, idle timeouts, and
 keep-alive sessions. Supports scheduled start/stop via cron expressions,
 custom actions (keystrokes, scrolling, scripts, application activation),
 and blackout periods.
 .
 Built with .NET 8 and Avalonia UI. Uses xdotool for X11 input simulation.
